<subSubSection pageId="41" pageNumber="435" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="41.[1396,2602,2270,3127]" pageId="41" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1398,1749,2935,2968]" pageId="41" pageNumber="435">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Muscular Broad-clawed Shrew has a highly restricted distribution, and virtually nothing is known aboutit due to its recent discovery; additional research is needed.
</paragraph>
